{
  "stem": "21786.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Obviously, the position I was in brought in unlimited amount of food, which I distributed not only to he and to most parents, but I was able to feed, I don't know how many dozens of people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For every dead person, if one reported the dead-- the death after the appel-- we got the ration for the dead person, which could be given to other people, three other people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got out-- outside of the camp, as I mentioned before, under circumstances which should be difficult to describe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For one, I had to bribe the SS men to keep-- leave us was alone, and mostly to be able to bring into the camp stuff, which certainly, would be seized and we would be severely punished, if not killed.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- let's say we were sent to this camp called Kanada, to bring from there blankets or, I don't know, something ridiculous like blouse, or some supplies, medical supplies.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the same time, we had to pick up a gold watch for the SS man who was at the gate, for he ordered, that he wanted a gold watch as a bribe.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we succeeded to bring in substantial amount of gasoline, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a rifle, couple of revolvers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was a underground-- mostly generated by the Russians, in the Russians camp, Russian prisoners of war, who were punished by being put then-- for escape, put to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And most were the communist underground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In a certain way, I was a member of this underground, for we didn't know each other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my only contribution and duty was to bring something which could help us in case that we will start an uprising.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
